               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390408-name-1608" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-1608" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-1608" type="surname" value="FREEMAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-1608" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM FREEMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a shoemaker, and live in Greenwich-road. I was sitting in my back parlour on the 10th of April, and in consequence of something ray wife told me I ran out of doors—I saw the prisoner rather running—I pursued him, and took hold of his collar—I said, what have you been taking? and at that moment I saw a boot fall from his person—I took it up, and with the boot and the prisoner I proceeded towards the station-house—Mr. Judson my neighbour came up—I wished him to go and see if there were not some more boots—be said, "If you will go I will hold the boy"—I went back, and close to where the prisoner had been standing when I took him, I found seven more boots—they were all mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390408-name-1609" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-1609" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-1609" type="surname" value="JUDSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-1609" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN JUDSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a licensed victualler. T was standing at my door cleaning a bird-cage—I saw the prisoner running along—I ran after him with the prosecutor—I saw one boot drop from the prisoner—I took him to the station-house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I went up the gateway, and the gentleman came and said, "Have yon stolen any thing?" I said, "No"—he took me op the gateway and found the boot.</p>
